Package iterator

Class pnodePQ

java.lang.Object
iterator.pnodePQ
Direct Known Subclasses:
pnodeSplayPQ
public abstract class pnodePQ
extends java.lang.Object
Implements a sorted binary tree. abstract methods enq and deq are used to add or remove elements from the tree.
